===Etymology 1===
{{zh-forms|alt=那}}
Written as {{zh-l|*那}} before the 20th century.

It is generally considered to be the fusion of {{och-l|奈何|how|id=1,1}} ({{zh-ref|Wang, 1990}}; {{zh-ref|Sun, 1992}}; {{zh-ref|Shimura, 1995}}), usually citing {{w|Gu Yanwu}}'s ({{w2|zh|顧炎武}}) commentary on ''{{w|Zuozhuan}}''. {{zh-ref|Lü (1985)}} distinguishes between “which” (choosing among several choices), which he derives from {{och-l|若|id=3}}, and “how” (asking for something), which he considers to be a fusion of {{och-l|若何|how|id=3,1}}.

